{"tid":352472,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人世間有一種遺憾，叫做得不到","createTime":"2017-08-08T20:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T01:41:44.000Z","uid":13378,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"048710da163c1d7c4a273572e7b63c5a33e728f4","tid":352472,"uid":13378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T20:40:35.000Z","msg":"因為得不到，我先會記住你好嘅地方<br />\n因為得不到，我先會咁珍惜以前嘅時間啊<br />\n因為得不到，我先渴望改變自己<br />\n因為得不到，我先念念不忘<br />\n<br />\n如果得到，你就唔會烙印係我嘅回憶入面<br />\n<br />\n人世間有一種遺憾，叫做得不到<br />\n<br />\n正正因為得不到，忘記了你的壞<br />\n<br />\n你亦顯得格外完美<br />\n<br />\n係愛呀<br />\n<br />\n亦係遺憾"},{"pid":"0361b3fea09c8d5f903ebe8df1dacad50d78d3c3","tid":352472,"uid":27915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T20:41:45.000Z","msg":"東邪西毒入面嘅梁嘉輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead5257f8d6abc7a6d676070c200cc6cfefb3bf5","tid":352472,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T21:22:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xgH-CTLfCxM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxgH-CTLfCxM&d=aOMh6bRR%2FW1IJbT9lu6pg0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=4b93bbfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xgH-CTLfCxM</a>"},{"pid":"df8a820585c4b2820b45d37aa4e66125fe0e9e4b","tid":352472,"uid":36402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T21:25:29.000Z","msg":"可是你 早已遠去 消失在人海"},{"pid":"55d69839a214f5ba3e2b788c3795b0f79cdb06b6","tid":352472,"uid":13378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T21:50:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可是你 早已遠去 消失在人海</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我尚駐足於那故所，極目天際，竟夜縵立，涙濡濕了衣裳，你回不來，可期，不可遇，此情，亦難再。<br />\n<br />\n很想再愛一次"},{"pid":"94ae7fe1016ec41cf61f37a5f65349c75507c767","tid":352472,"uid":67976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T22:02:32.000Z","msg"